{"tid":632332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"崇拜馬克思主義嘅全部都係憎人富貴厭人窮嘅傻閪","createTime":"2018-04-17T09:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T10:03:09.000Z","uid":99568,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53f93d608b69226162dbf60234c4d96afd806484","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"馬克思把資本主義時期的人與人關係丑化成你死我活的鬥爭，而把共產主義未來美化成人人大公無私的神仙狀態，這些都是不值一駁的謊言。<br />\n<br />\n無論共產黨人給馬克思加上多少美麗的桂冠，政治家、哲學家、經濟學家、革命理論家、革命導師等等，其最本質特徵就是一個反對上帝的撒旦教徒，他的所言所行都是圍繞這一主題展開的。<br />\n<br />\n1847年由於一項複印機專利糾紛，馬克思需要在仲裁人面前按著《聖經》發誓他說的是真話，誰知這樣一個法律程序卻大大的惹惱了他，他抗議說他永遠不會這樣侮辱自己。彼時的馬克思早已不再熱衷於抨擊宗教，但從他竟然拒絕接觸《聖經》這一極端行為來看，他心裡對上帝的仇恨是何等的根深柢固，這也從另一側面說明，他的主要著作不過是為了讓人遠離上帝而設計的種種誘惑罷了。<br />\n<br />\n2004年出版的《九評共產黨》，對共產黨是人間最大邪教做了精闢的論述，馬克思主義作為邪教的思想原理，自然也是邪惡無比的。這裡我們只簡單探討一下其主要學說的荒謬性。<br />\n<br />\n信奉馬克思的人缺乏才智<br />\n<br />\n著名學者仲維光在《五四、馬克思主義及中國知識界問題》一文中指出，「一個人年輕的時候信奉馬克思主義是因為他有熱血，在三十歲的時候還信奉馬克思主義，則說明他缺乏才智。」文章以弗格林、波普為例，在經歷了初期的肯定到最後堅決否定的認識過程，他們的共同結論是：「馬克思是知識分子中的騙子。」<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，較早認識馬克思邪惡本質的人，卻是另外一個邪惡之徒：希特勒。楊豐在《希特勒與馬克思主義》一文中指出，希特勒在《我的奮鬥》中稱馬克思主義是「精神的瘟疫」，是「由自私和仇恨構成」的一種「斷絕人性的毀滅性學說」。「馬克思主義否認人的個性價值，因此抽去了人性存在的基礎和文化精髓。從根本上看，這一學說將導致人類智慧所能構想的一切秩序統統崩潰，導致這個星球上的生命統統毀滅。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n較早認識馬克思邪惡本質的人，卻是另外一個邪惡之徒：希特勒。（Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n希特勒還發現共產黨人利用無產階級專政來取代民主的妙處，他對馬克思主義的深刻洞悉並不說明他偉大，而是可見他超凡的狡黠和機智。他曾表示，他那個「謊言說一千遍就等於真理」的強盜邏輯，就是從共產黨人那學來的，把「獸性的殘忍和無法想像的謊言結合在一起」，「宣傳加暴力」，這跟中共所說的「筆桿子加槍桿子」一樣，都源於馬克思學說。<br />\n<br />\n被扭曲的現實與不可能的未來<br />\n<br />\n在講資本主義社會時，馬克思故意誇大人性惡的一面，認為「到目前為止的一切社會的歷史都是階級鬥爭的歷史」，不過這是違背事實的偽命題。數千年來人類不斷認識自然，認識自我，認識社會，人類以國家、民族、地區、團體、個人之間的競爭與合作，不斷的積累著物質和精神領域的文化與文明，相比之下，階級的區分並不明顯，與階級鬥爭相反的是，絕大多數時間裡，不同階層的組合構成了一個立體的和諧社會，人們在各種階層裡平靜的生活。<br />\n<br />\n馬克思把人與人之間的關係扭曲成「人人為敵，你死我活」的階級對立，分割了人類的共通情誼和善良情感，把有別於動物的人性，分割成了比獸性還要獸性的對立，同時又在「解放全人類」的謊言下，誘發人性中自私陰暗殘暴的一面。人們把少量的暴力行為稱為恐怖活動，而馬克思卻把大規模的暴力行動美化成了革命，這種強盜邏輯無疑是人類思想的毒瘤。<br />\n<br />\n在講共產主義未來時，馬克思又片面誇大人性美化的一面，強調人類理性的力量，認為人人都能大公無私的把勞動當成第一需要，整個社會資源能夠無限的增大，最後實現各盡所能，按需要分配。<br />\n<br />\n不過這樣完美的仙境能在人間立足嗎？只有神才能做到這些吧。<br />\n<br />\n如今中共依然奉行馬克思<br />\n<br />\n這樣一個前後矛盾、建立在歪曲的現實和不可能的未來基礎上的假說，怎麼能夠成為「放諸四海而準」的真理呢？毫無疑問，這背後有著人類看不見的力量在推它，否則它是無法迷惑那麼多人的。<br />\n<br />\n有人認為，馬克思提出的理論是好的，只是後來人錯誤的運用了它，就跟大陸老百姓過去常說的，中央的政策是好的，只是下面的人把經念歪了。其實這是種錯覺，共產主義從其根源和老祖宗那裡就錯了。<br />\n<br />\n比如文化大革命，如今中共把罪過推到四人幫或某個人身上，好像只有偶爾一時的失誤，其實馬克思早就提出，共產黨人必須摧毀人類現有的一切制度，包括其文化傳統，文革只是按照馬克思的要求在進行而已。中共搞大躍進也是按照馬克思原教旨理論進行的。既然共產黨人能「推翻舊世界、創立新天地」，成為未來的「救世主」，那跑步進入共產主義社會又有什麼不可能的呢？自大狂從馬克思開始，一直是共產黨人的共性。<br />\n<br />\n有人說現在中共早就拋棄馬克思了，這話其實是中共散布的煙幕彈。用鄧小平的話說，共產黨的核心問題從來都沒有動搖過，如果說中共有些變化，那只是把以前的謊言遮羞布拋棄得更多，更加赤裸裸地挑戰人類文明而已<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本而家呢個世界已經冇曬國家係真係實行社會主義， 歷史已經告訴咗我哋 呢個主意係唔會work， 同埋唔好成日攞北歐打飛機， 因為北歐 嘅國企 公司十分強大， 北區地理位置 有好多石油氣天然資源, 再加上 人民嘅 質數十分之高， 如果香港 實行北區嗰種福利主義社會主義， 成班低質香港人一定好食懶非呃綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a104d9c9f2e03c90bc386cea7c49a03ed2aabb5","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"小弟只係一名小學雞， 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604c55b785b98188905a874cc68b591c976f2d7f","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11d8ec1fb860a3b883db9e0090443c593fa75e47","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"你哋成班撚樣成日話 唔好 攞自由市場講， 但係你哋唔明白自由市場嘅重要性， 如果香港唔係自由市場， 點會有咁多大公司設資喺香港, 點會提供咗咁多工作崗位？ 到時你哋連屎都冇得食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8af19c22e286543d42fe28495b0a690b2ea6a28","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d10aed0cf1858f8b954d4fff40396dd471b944","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"有競爭就有進步"},{"pid":"c1ee5e0459a9e82ff7d8da1797eb69858c0f6ee9","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3224dbcb04960d97d58a7f66cb8bb5bafa1992ae","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ea9f4c161910d6285ed6f92d493c039446c6b5f3","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae1e3af3ee8621d35b7756d45e4d9c40047e6ebd","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee5b82831e8d075be6a64d9d3c24e96b737961d9","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ae4bee76eaace40bba16254695c299587c6a4cd","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cadbf0ed766df3448b55fe4f2cabe4c9fd0a7e8","tid":632332,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">懷疑五毛Me係鬼仔#99568冒警</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/624248/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/624248/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"ee7c136311586daf9be7ddeecffd36bb2563f5c9","tid":632332,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cadbf0ed766df3448b55fe4f2cabe4c9fd0a7e8","tid":632332,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">懷疑五毛Me係鬼仔#99568冒警</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/624248/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/624248/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=edcfbd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001544_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001544_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d496bf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001551_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001551_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8b04e57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛Me係鬼仔#99568底已起</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android[/quote][quote]事緣: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1</a><br />\n會員on99屌喇星開post起鳩個小學雞底 由於睇唔過眼<br />\n亦見到佢自爆左youtube ac, 決定用少少時間試下起佢底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會員on99屌喇星 youtube ac: pc 9527<br />\n竟然連接左google+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功左第一步<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/103914_8254a4657f68510fb01fac469b5a9b42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F103914_8254a4657f68510fb01fac469b5a9b42.png&h=b2294ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁既資料太唔足夠 亦好容易起錯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再慢慢睇下youtube ac比到D咩我地 發現原來on99屌喇星upload過幾條片<br />\n其中一條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104145_32d3ca5e23f4ccf1e4c8660c40e75f33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104145_32d3ca5e23f4ccf1e4c8660c40e75f33.png&h=2706f2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104151_0a7b8575f81e6d28645879810e6f43a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104151_0a7b8575f81e6d28645879810e6f43a9.png&h=8b057f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信該留言者熟悉片主 亦都透露左pc 9527亦即係on99屌喇星叫Joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我地就開始用google+比既資料去起底 <br />\n首先係Tam Hiu Sze小姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104408_bdd7c437366c101ea2b7ab2f606a469e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104408_bdd7c437366c101ea2b7ab2f606a469e.png&h=84ac15b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左確保無搵錯人 我係Tam Hiu Sze小姐既friend list試下搵唔搵到common friend<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104435_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104435_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=b02aba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果成功搵到Hoi Kit Leung<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104540_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104540_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=dc576784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再搵到Cody Lam<br />\n<br />\n已經代表無起錯 不過重點主角都係依位叫呀Joe既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104726_bbf4bbb47f12200df3f5be6765c24aad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104726_bbf4bbb47f12200df3f5be6765c24aad.png&h=bb2303cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104734_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104734_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=f2ead5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104740_e29efbe021d12549075b6b01f41993eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104740_e29efbe021d12549075b6b01f41993eb.jpg&h=0a176f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104747_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104747_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=0fc3268b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾位friend list都不約而同有依位Joe Lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105148_a9fc6e56641b97a4f42197d18d69f16f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105148_a9fc6e56641b97a4f42197d18d69f16f.jpg&h=2fbbbffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Joe Lee friend list亦都有Andy Lee <br />\n咁多資料加埋已經幾肯定會員on99屌喇星就係Joe Lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再保守D 我地睇埋Joe Lee既Facebook<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105342_49829455611ff6eaed3d12c1c0468dd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105342_49829455611ff6eaed3d12c1c0468dd0.png&h=d40766c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係倫敦讀緊書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105355_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105355_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=5724e527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105411_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105411_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=b7c5f033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都同會員on99屌喇星一樣好關注時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後就係會員on99屌喇星出場喇！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105515_20fd42213f37387d37674cc384319170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105515_20fd42213f37387d37674cc384319170.png&h=cbc40d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105520_8cf4b6fc0feb75748a28801a6e7aa0d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105520_8cf4b6fc0feb75748a28801a6e7aa0d6.png&h=80ec764c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於無其他相 透過2張相既推測<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105551_c2e758ec1d4b65886c2e24eeddbe75c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105551_c2e758ec1d4b65886c2e24eeddbe75c2.jpg&h=4a54c7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會員on99屌喇星就係前排中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2136324617e260674deb561563eb45229fe55f","tid":632332,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee7c136311586daf9be7ddeecffd36bb2563f5c9","tid":632332,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cadbf0ed766df3448b55fe4f2cabe4c9fd0a7e8","tid":632332,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">懷疑五毛Me係鬼仔#99568冒警</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/624248/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/624248/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=edcfbd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001544_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001544_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d496bf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001551_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001551_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8b04e57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛Me係鬼仔#99568底已起</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android[/quote][quote]事緣: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https